metadata.name: Paper & Pencils
metadata.description:
!!!! 1st song of the Tarotsings February NFT Marathon !!!! 

The music I am sharing with you for the next 28 days is a reflection of the most vulnerable part of who I am as a human being. Think of it as a diary written of songs essentially. There is no overthinking or strategy involved in the making of this music, just pure creative flow - exposing the most raw side of me as an artist.

"Paper & Pencils" is lowkey a metaphor for all the creative ideas that flow through me & the process of turning all my manifestations into reality by just taking the leap & following my gut. I've really began to learn that believing in yourself is the key, and any locked door is just merely an illusion <3 

Highest bidder get's the first spot in the Tarotsings Astral Realm!

It flows  
And it goes 
Composing  
Like a puzzle with no picture 

It grows on you slow  
Fairly quickly 
Til it turns to something you just used to know 

Patience  
I tread  
I’m running in my head 
Goin slow through the tunnel vision  
In a maze of a last minute decision  
Paper & pencils in my bed 

Sketch it off of memory 
Just before they pass  
They don’t last 
Anyway 

Every inch of space 
Put way too much weight 
On what you’re gonna say
